("
  Flexible if/else construct using method chaining.  
  
  ```
  if(cond) ( ... true part ... ) ?:
  if(cond) ( ... part 2 ... ) ?: 
  ( ... final option ...)
  ```
  
  The `else` method returns the selected value, the intermediate methods return some intermediate
  object.
") ⇒ (cond) ↦ (then) ↦ cond {
  true = {
    x.else if(new cond) = (new then) ↦ x
    else() = then
  }
  false = {
    else if(new cond) = if(new cond)
    else(fallback) = fallback 
  }

}